'''布雷肯'''（{{lang-en|Brecon}}，{{lang-cy|Aberhonddu}}）是位於[[英國|英國]][[威爾斯|威爾斯]]中部[[波伊斯|波伊斯]]的一座[[城鎮|城鎮]]，有人口7,901人<ref>{{Citation | url = http://www.neighbourhood.statistics.gov.uk/dissemination/viewFullDataset.do?instanceSelection=03070&productId=779&$ph=60_61&datasetInstanceId=3070&startColumn=1&numberOfColumns=8&containerAreaId=790565 | publisher = Office for National Statistics | title = Census | year = 2001 | contribution = Parish Headcounts: Powys | accessdate = 2009-11-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110613032101/http://www.neighbourhood.statistics.gov.uk/dissemination/viewFullDataset.do?instanceSelection=03070&productId=779&$ph=60_61&datasetInstanceId=3070&startColumn=1&numberOfColumns=8&containerAreaId=790565 | archive-date = 2011-06-13 | dead-url = yes }}.</ref>，布雷肯是波伊斯的第三大城市，也是一座旅遊城市和軍事城市。
